{"tid":541324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"萬寧事件，最錯根本就係PR","createTime":"2018-01-26T09:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T15:06:14.000Z","uid":14201,"like":99,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c8d17c62e26f5b3e795bfb5b8fc4b3f09f97eb4b","tid":541324,"uid":14201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T09:52:26.000Z","msg":"一開始就學人玩強硬，話尊重法治，咁就畀佢地釀成第一場公關災難。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/26/173449_5da94d9ae0d172a68adc7d89759bb1bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F26%2F173449_5da94d9ae0d172a68adc7d89759bb1bc.png&h=9c4a23c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n汲取返上次個教訓，今次行返溫和路線，已經太遲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/26/173605_158772f8550578c075a8203cf0422624.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F26%2F173605_158772f8550578c075a8203cf0422624.png&h=923ddcb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完單新聞，連個官都話個阿婆唔係可信，相信萬寧就係覺得自己大條道理就寸寸貢。<br />\n<br />\n但係佢地完全忽略咗佢啲客同網民情感因素：阿婆，執垃圾，半盲，連鎖財團，大話保安。<br />\n<br />\n兩篇聲明個timing錯哂，如果一開始未判就柔少少，話深感同情慰問阿婆，最少唔會畀人屌得咁勁。之後法庭再係有疑點下判無罪嘅時候，話尊重法庭，相信唔會再係咁一面倒咁支持個阿婆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家話萬寧班PR應該慶幸未畀人炒，雖則話director同ceo點頭先岀得街，但係岀稿條友，真係腦裝屎。"},{"pid":"91e0176d5c2030dd915023663669f08c5ede9e2f","tid":541324,"uid":4517,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T09:54:39.000Z","msg":"你係控方證人點可能深表同情被告"},{"pid":"50f712bc6be099f6a6296258546700d25ed20633","tid":541324,"uid":102078,"like":10,"dislike":20,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T09:56:39.000Z","msg":"阿婆就大撚晒?<br />\n似老賣老,任意妄為?"},{"pid":"8057033369915ca573f6c09ec750dc3c34503b01","tid":541324,"uid":14201,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"91e0176d5c2030dd915023663669f08c5ede9e2f","tid":54132